⭐[Python Visualization Tool Kits]
*link:
√ Whole/ https://www.jianshu.com/p/62027a72a794
√ Matplotlib/ https://juejin.cn/post/6844903832825102350

Aim：找到合适的库，
- Matplotlib, 
  [√]绘图风格比较简约
  [×]代码量较大，绘图速度慢，交互性不强
- - Seaborn 封装了很多统计函数, 相对美观
- - pandas.tools.plotting 对dataframe直接进行绘图
- - ggplot + R language, 借助了/图形语法的概念
- - 数据的空间分布：Basemap, Cartopy, geopandas
- Based on JS,
  [√]交互可视化
  - Bokeh & Holoviews
  - plotly
  - Cufflins
  - GeoViews 可视化地理数据，可与HoloViews对象混合和匹配
  - Folium 绘制空间数据神库
  - Altair 统计可视化, 围绕pandas dataframe构建
  


⭐[可视化图的基本要素与选择]
- 3 basic elements
  - label, title, legend
  
- When to use which ?
  - bar, hist -> Show the distribution
  - scatter -> discrete points
  - stackplot -> 比较像层积岩
  - pie -> Percentage
  
  

